user_prompt_template:
Analyze the following job posting and extract the security clearance requirement:

Job Title: {title}
Company: {company}
Location: {location}
Description: {description}

Please return a JSON response with the following structure:
{
  "clearance_level": "TS/SCI|TS|Secret|Confidential|None",
  "confidence": 0.95,
  "reasoning": "explanation of why this clearance level was identified",
  "keywords_found": ["keyword1", "keyword2"],
  "additional_requirements": ["requirement1", "requirement2"]
}

Clearance level options:
- TS/SCI: Top Secret/Sensitive Compartmented Information
- TS: Top Secret
- Secret: Secret clearance
- Confidential: Confidential clearance
- None: No clearance requirement found

If multiple clearance levels are mentioned, choose the highest level required.
